document_data.mainbody:
'''''On the Lookout!''''' is a tournament module set in ''Malatra – Living Jungle'' using the ''Dungeons & Dragons'' 2{{rd}} edition ruleset. It is part of the ''[[Living Jungle]]'' series of adventures published for the RPGA Network. The adventure is intended for low-level and mid-level characters.

{{Quote|''Far below the [[Valley of Spirits]] has evolved a species of [[ant]] unlike any seen on the [[Malatran Plateau]]. Much
larger than common ants, they are single-minded carnivores who devour anything in their path. They poured into the Valley of the Spirits itself. Now they march across Malatra, leaving a trail of death and destruction in their wake.''|}}

